üåê REST API Endpoints
HTTP Method	Endpoint	Description	Status Codes
POST	/students	Register new student	201 Created, 409 Conflict
GET	/students	Get all students	200 OK, 204 No Content
GET	/students/{id}	Get student by ID	200 OK, 404 Not Found
PUT	/students/{id}	Update student	200 OK, 404 Not Found
DELETE	/students/{id}	Delete student	200 OK, 404 Not Found
