üìä HTTP Status Codes Used
Status Code	Description	When Used
200 OK	Success	GET (found), PUT (updated), DELETE (deleted)
201 Created	Resource created	POST (new student registered)
204 No Content	Success but no data	GET all students (empty list)
404 Not Found	Resource not found	GET/PUT/DELETE (student doesn't exist)
409 Conflict	Duplicate resource	POST (student ID already exists)
