üß™ Complete Postman Test Sequence
Test Scenario 1: Happy Path
1.	‚úÖ POST /students - Register student 101 ‚Üí 201 Created
2.	‚úÖ POST /students - Register student 102 ‚Üí 201 Created
3.	‚úÖ GET /students - View all ‚Üí 200 OK (shows 2 students)
4.	‚úÖ GET /students/101 - Search ‚Üí 200 OK (found)
5.	‚úÖ PUT /students/101 - Update ‚Üí 200 OK (updated)
6.	‚úÖ DELETE /students/102 - Delete ‚Üí 200 OK (deleted)
7.	‚úÖ GET /students - View all ‚Üí 200 OK (shows 1 student)
Test Scenario 2: Error Handling
1.	‚ùå POST /students - Duplicate ID 101 ‚Üí 409 Conflict
2.	‚ùå GET /students/999 - Not found ‚Üí 404 Not Found
3.	‚ùå PUT /students/999 - Update non-existent ‚Üí 404 Not Found
4.	‚ùå DELETE /students/999 - Delete non-existent ‚Üí 404 Not Found
5.	‚úÖ GET /students - Empty list ‚Üí 204 No Content (if all deleted)
