üéØ Key Takeaways
1.	‚úÖ @RestController - For building REST APIs
2.	‚úÖ ResponseEntity - Control HTTP status codes
3.	‚úÖ @Service - Business logic layer
4.	‚úÖ @RequestBody - Convert JSON to Java object
5.	‚úÖ @PathVariable - Extract ID from URL
6.	‚úÖ HTTP Methods - POST, GET, PUT, DELETE for CRUD
7.	‚úÖ Status Codes - 200, 201, 204, 404, 409
8.	‚úÖ Postman - Test REST APIs
9.	‚úÖ In-Memory Storage - ArrayList for learning
10.	‚úÖ Layered Architecture - Controller ‚Üí Service ‚Üí Storage

